{%- comment -%}
  whl_callout.liquid — a highlighted .whl-callout box. `text` is Markdown, so
  editors write plain text (bold with **…**) with no <div>. Usage:
    {% include whl_callout.liquid text=page.intro_callout %}
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if include.text and include.text != '' -%}
  <div class="whl-callout">{{ include.text | markdownify }}</div>
{%- endif -%}
